article_id:1415,category_name:News,title_name:Gala Dragalia Is Now Live!,image_path:,message:<div>Gala Dragalia went live <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1593410400"></span>!</div><div><br></div><div>What is Gala Dragalia?</div><div>・The initial appearance rate for 5★ adventurers and dragons will be boosted to 6% from the standard 4%! If you get a 5★ summon or 5★ featured summon, the appearance rate will return to the initial 6%.</div><div><span style="color: rgb(226, 80, 65);">Note: The newly added 5★ adventurers Eugene (water) and Catherine (water), as well as 5★ dragon Styx (water), will also appear in the next summon showcase.</span></div><div><br></div><div>Newly featured adventurers and dragons:</div><div>■Adventurers</div><div>5★ Eugene (water/sword)</div><div>5★ Catherine (water/lance)</div><div><br></div><div>■Dragons</div><div>5★ Gala Cat S&igrave;th (shadow)</div><div>5★ Styx (water)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia appearance rates:</div><div>5★ total: 6.00%</div><div>5★ featured total: 2.60% (Adventurers: 1.00%, Dragons: 1.60%)</div><div>5★ standard total: 3.40% (Adventurers: 2.00%, Dragons: 1.40%)</div><div>4★ standard total: 16.00% (Adventurers: 8.55%,　Dragons: 7.45%)</div><div>3★ standard total: 78.00% (Adventurers: 47.00%, Dragons: 31.00%)</div><div><br></div><div>Gala Dragalia active period:</div><div><span class="local_date" data-local_date="1593410400"></span> to <span class="local_date" data-local_date="1593755940"></span></div><div><br></div><div>Get a closer look at the newly featured adventurers and dragons below.</div><div><br></div><div>Featured dragons:</div><div>
