	<dl><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png"></span><span>(Shadow) Skillful Trickery II</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Shadow: <br>increases the damage dealt by the user's<br>next 15 skills by 180% at the start of quests.<br>Every 25-hit combo will increase the damage<br>dealt by an additional skill by 180%. A maximum<br>of 15 of this skill damage increasing effect can<br>be stored for use, and any excess will be discarded.</div></dd><dt><span><img src="https://dragalialost.akamaized.net/attached/information/images/318c94807552d34eb43eebac3f21952f2.png"></span><span>(Shadow) Ending Shapeshift = Skillful Trickery II</span></dt><dd><div>If the user is attuned to Shadow: <br>increases the damage dealt by the user's<br>next eight skills by 180% when the user's<br>shapeshift is undone.</div></dd></dl></div></div></div><div><br></div><div>■Regarding Gala Cat S&igrave;th&#39;s Attacks<br>While shapeshifted, Gala Cat S&igrave;th&#39;s standard attacks deal damage to enemies in the area and inflict sleep.</div><div><br>■Regarding Buff Count<br>Even if the buff applied by Gala Cat S&igrave;th&#39;s (Shadow) Skillful Trickery I/II ability has stacked, it will count as a single buff for skills that are altered by the number of buffs affecting the user.</div><div><br></div><div>
